  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK322">
<l>pakuttuṇṭu palluyi rōmputa ṉūlōr</l>
<l>tokuttavaṟṟu ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The chief of all (the virtues) which authors have summed up, is the partaking of food that has been shared with others, and the preservation of the mainfold life of other creatures.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
